item.title: For all your proxy help and questions!
item.dc:creator: @edycus edycus
item.description:
@edycus wrote:

ok, look at this file name. Run-Bot.bat

Edit it’s content to look like

@echo off
title Running Bot WITH PROXY
java -DsocksProxyHost=81.172.3.234 -DsocksProxyPort=1080-noverify -Xmx500m -cp .;./OUTPUT;./OUTPUT/unrenamed.jar;./BotClasses; Bot
pause

81.172.3.234 is the server and 1080is the port these are the items you will need to change on you file

The site 81.172.3.234 works for me but very slow. You need to get one of the PRoxy programs that are mentioned, The y will help you find a proxy closer to you. If you get a proxy in Japan it will get lagggg bad.

The proxy needs to support Socks5 - (at least that’s what I’m told)

Whne you get a error it mean eather the proxy is not there anymore or the proxy doesn’t support Socks5 which mean it want work with Runescape.

Message me for more info I’ll try and help you find a proxy in your area.
